{"word":"συνεπιμελέομαι","slug":"συνεπιμελέομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>συνεπιμελέομαι</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><el>μέλομαι</el>\n<p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to join in taking care of</i> or <i>attending to</i>, <el>τινος</el> <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <el>ς. τῆς στρατιᾶς</el> <i>to have joint charge of</i> the army, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <a href='S:absolute, absolutely'>absol.</a>, <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b><p/>"}]}